item.title: CVE-2022-4654|2024-08-03T01:48:39.735Z -- unknown -- pricing%20tables%20wordpress%20plugin
item.description: The Pricing Tables WordPress Plugin WordPress plugin before 3.2.3 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack.
